<br>
Example (hypotheical from how I understand what they have said): You might have 25/24 (numbers not reversed) 1 hs weapon that has +10 MR +10 FR +10 CR. You also have a 25/24 a hs that has +10 MR +10 DR +10 PR.<br>
<br>
Obviously in plane of decay you probably want the PR DR while if they add Sol Ro's plane you would want more FR.<br>
<br>
You will probably still want main tanks with mad taunt weapons that have come out of Velious but if you aren't MT then to make sure the cleric can still heal him you want the resists over the mad taunt weapon to not be a mana sponge.<br>
<br>
That is how I think it will be, so probably you still see you WS' and your lammies as demanded items for tanks as the move from mid to post 50 levels. The yak will still be a great twink item or one of those things that the brand new player can aspire to get as a decent weapon. They may be lower in price but then again there may be a demand from new player (and returning) that come to check out the new expansion. <p><center>Sjoc Straupp<BR>Knight of<BR>Heroes<BR>
